It doesn't matter.

53
00:04:02,834 --> 00:04:04,799
Anyway...

54
00:04:19,294 --> 00:04:21,999
I really don't mind.

55
00:04:22,833 --> 00:04:26,667
My life has already hit rock bottom anyway.

56
00:04:27,701 --> 00:04:30,009
But you're different.

57
00:04:30,009 --> 00:04:32,319
You can make a comeback.

58
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:35,042
