70
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:31,942
I also hoped you'd celebrate my birthday with me.

71
00:05:31,942 --> 00:05:34,678
I also wanted to taste the food you made.

72
00:05:34,678 --> 00:05:36,592
Did you?

73
