00:09:08,917 --> 00:09:10,742
Hai Nuo.

115
00:09:12,335 --> 00:09:15,234
Tang Mi, what are you doing here?

116
00:09:20,377 --> 00:09:22,050
Here, this is for you.

117
00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:25,352
Thank you. By the way, this is for you.

118
00:09:25,352 --> 00:09:27,868
Thank you. That's so kind of you.

119
00:09:27,868 --> 00:09:29,618
I'll go put it down.

120
00:09:32,210 --> 00:09:37,192
By the way, what brings you to Kinmen so suddenly?

121
00:09:38,218 --> 00:09:40,701
After the reality show incident,

122
00:09:40,701 --> 00:09:43,125
I decided to leave that uncomfortable environment

123
00:09:43,125 --> 00:09:45,142
and pursue what I want to do.

124
00:09:47,942 --> 00:09:49,000
That makes sense.

125
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,867
After the reality show,

126
00:09:50,867 --> 00:09:53,359
you must have been under a lot of pressure.

127
00:09:55,494 --> 00:09:58,400
But why did you choose Kinmen?

128
00:10:02,527 --> 00:10:06,084
After seeing how Yin Mo changed for the better

129
00:10:06,084 --> 00:10:08,134
since he came here,

130
00:10:08,701 --> 00:10:12,767
I've made up my mind to start afresh here.

131
00:10:12,767 --> 00:10:15,645
I want to truly feel what life is all about,

132
00:10:15,645 --> 00:10:20,001
go back to my old days of filming, create freely,

133
00:10:20,001 --> 00:10:22,042
and share my experiences and discoveries

134
00:10:22,042 --> 00:10:24,359
with more people.

135
00:10:25,867 --> 00:10:29,967
What will you start with?

136
00:10:34,018 --> 00:10:35,942
Ever since I was a child,

137
00:10:35,942 --> 00:10:38,092
I've dreamed of opening a café.

138
00:10:38,092 --> 00:10:43,042
I plan to start with a local café, learn step by step,

139
00:10:43,042 --> 00:10:45,909
- We're here.
- And document my journey as I go.

140
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:50,460
Hai Nuo, you brought a guest here for coffee?

141
00:10:50,460 --> 00:10:52,459
You Cai.

142
00:10:52,459 --> 00:10:54,599
You met during the reality show.

143
00:10:56,435 --> 00:10:58,742
Hello, I'm Tang Mi.

144
00:10:58,742 --> 00:11:00,668
Sorry. I didn't recognize you.

145
00:11:00,668 --> 00:11:01,799
Welcome. Come on in.

146
00:11:01,799 --> 00:11:03,734
Okay.

147
00:11:03,734 --> 00:11:05,509
Thank you.

148
00:11:06,294 --> 00:11:09,276
Hai Nuo, why don't you take Ms. Tang to sit in the back?

149
00:11:09,276 --> 00:11:10,661
It's more private and no one will disturb you.

150
00:11:10,661 --> 00:11:14,876
You Cai, I brought Tang Mi here today to meet you.

151
00:11:14,876 --> 00:11:17,184
To meet me? Why?

152
00:11:17,184 --> 00:11:19,535
You've been in the coffee business for years.

153
00:11:19,535 --> 00:11:22,292
Have you thought about taking on an apprentice?

154
00:11:23,678 --> 00:11:25,327
